title: Tin Foil Hat Ep 17: Tibetan Book of The Dead with Greg Carlwood
description:
Thank you for tuning into another episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli. This episode, Sam and Ryan, welcome back from the Higherside Chats Podcast, Greg Carlwood. This is easily one of my favorite podcast episodes I have ever done. I so enjoyed this discussion with Greg and Ryan!
On this episode we discuss...
1) Trump and April 26th
2) The After Life
3) Psychedelics
4) Heaven and Hell
5) The Tibetan Book of the Dead
6) The Three Bardos
7) The Five Groups of Rebirth
